akka.testkit.typed

Class TestKit

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.testkit.typed.TestKit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TestKitBase

    public class TestKit
extends java.lang.Object
implements TestKitBase
    Testkit for typed actors. Extending this removes some boiler plate when testing typed actors.

    If a test can't extend then use the TestKitBase trait
